00:32:39.560 --> 00:32:42.460
of give a little bit more
visual life to the way

00:32:42.460 --> 00:32:46.640
that he was telling the
story but anything goes.

00:32:46.640 --> 00:32:49.840
&gt;&gt; When you see different
