00:34:05.910 --> 00:34:09.810
working with people who are not
musically literate is exhausting

00:34:09.810 --> 00:34:13.470
for me so there are people who love
to do that and I'm not one of them

00:34:13.470 --> 00:34:15.570
so that's why I have
music directors.

00:34:15.570 --> 00:34:21.740
And you know, the joys
of working with musicians

00:34:21.740 --> 00:34:24.720
who really can just read the
material down that's like oh great,

00:34:24.720 --> 00:34:26.750 position:56%
we get to go past the sort of basics

00:34:26.750 --> 00:34:30.010
