00:36:29.510 --> 00:36:32.240
which is weird for a writer to
say but I think I'm a writer

00:36:32.240 --> 00:36:35.900 position:56%
who most enjoys sort of interpreting
the work as it goes which isn't

00:36:35.900 --> 00:36:39.420
to say I want to be a
